# CHAT API ENDPOINTS - IMPLEMENTATION RULES

## Chat API Overview
- **Base Path:** `/api/chat/`
- **Total Endpoints:** 9 endpoints
- **Authentication:** JWT Bearer Token Required
- **Real-time:** WebSocket support for live messaging
- **Rate Limiting:** 50 requests/minute per user

## MANDATORY Chat Endpoints Implementation

